eNCA report has confirmed that images showing black DA supporters transported in cattle trucks to attend it&#8217;s manifesto launch are legit. The report also confirms that the DA paid people to fill the stadium.Initially the DA denied that the images were legit and claimed that someone had photoshopped and circulated them. But the person who actually took the pictures has come forward to confirm that they are indeed legit.The pictures were taken by a community activist from Prieska in the Northern Cape on the 27th of April. They went viral of Facebook and triggered racism accusations against the DA. comments